      "chapter_id": null,
      "title": null,
      "body": "Focar no processo, não no resultado — o resultado é subproduto do processo bem feito.",
      "kind": "hipotese",
      "free_tags": [],
      "created_at": "2026-07-05T00:48:31.192006+00:00",
      "themes": [
        {
          "id": "7098acea-a6a9-4fba-951a-a861278a3ae2",
          "slug": "proposito",
          "label": "Propósito"
        },
        {
          "id": "2245f69c-e13f-45b5-848e-d79688d92909",
          "slug": "competencia",
          "label": "Competência"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "8d961995-1b0d-405c-8e30-9876abe4691a",
      "book_id": "a8ef8ece-5c7f-40f9-86bc-de1ddb50e7c5",
      "chapter_id": null,
      "title": null,
      "body": "Você sente medo, mas não precisa obedecê-lo — a emoção informa, não comanda.",
      "kind": "hipotese",
      "free_tags": [],
      "created_at": "2026-07-05T00:48:31.192006+00:00",
      "themes": [
        {
          "id": "82d7190e-818e-427b-ad09-c22e996a3733",
          "slug": "medo",
          "label": "Medo"
        },
        {
          "id": "3ec9df17-f6ac-458b-813d-f1ffeb03be5e",
          "slug": "autocontrole",
          "label": "Autocontrole"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "b85be473-4760-4712-acc3-b6d36694b292",
      "book_id": "a8ef8ece-5c7f-40f9-86bc-de1ddb50e7c5",
      "chapter_id": null,
      "title": null,
      "body": "A responsabilidade individual é a base — o ambiente melhora quando o indivíduo assume o próprio peso.",
      "kind": "hipotese",
      "free_tags": [],
      "created_at": "2026-07-05T00:48:31.192006+00:00",
      "themes": [
        {
          "id": "71c544be-86cb-4b38-a754-0cae1abda757",
          "slug": "lideranca",
          "label": "Liderança"
        },
        {
          "id": "10530066-72f0-48df-9ff7-0a6d930515c5",
          "slug": "responsabilidade",
          "label": "Responsabilidade"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "7cf11149-c275-415b-bc67-e3a1bd9489bf",
      "book_id": "a8ef8ece-5c7f-40f9-86bc-de1ddb50e7c5",
      "chapter_id": null,
      "title": null,
      "body": "Competência verdadeira não precisa de demonstração constante — a arrogância é sinal de insegurança, não de força.",
      "kind": "hipotese",
      "free_tags": [],
      "created_at": "2026-07-05T00:48:31.192006+00:00",
      "themes": [
        {
          "id": "abfbc107-783c-472a-82e4-499aa36e9a18",
          "slug": "ego",
          "label": "Ego"
        },
        {
          "id": "2245f69c-e13f-45b5-848e-d79688d92909",
          "slug": "competencia",
          "label": "Competência"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "0e14b2e4-de87-4843-a4b7-e6bab522a960",
      "book_id": "a8ef8ece-5c7f-40f9-86bc-de1ddb50e7c5",
      "chapter_id": null,
      "title": null,
      "body": "Encontrar significado é o que sustenta diante do sofrimento — sem propósito, qualquer crítica destrói.",
      "kind": "hipotese",
      "free_tags": [],
      "created_at": "2026-07-05T00:48:31.192006+00:00",
      "themes": [
        {
          "id": "0e291322-2d47-485e-bef4-c46543d059e6",
          "slug": "sofrimento",
          "label": "Sofrimento"
        },
        {
          "id": "82d7190e-818e-427b-ad09-c22e996a3733",
          "slug": "medo",
          "label": "Medo"
        },
        {
          "id": "7098acea-a6a9-4fba-951a-a861278a3ae2",
          "slug": "proposito",
          "label": "Propósito"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "a16cfd3c-f7df-46bf-9ae9-217764d9b073",
      "book_id": "a8ef8ece-5c7f-40f9-86bc-de1ddb50e7c5",
      "chapter_id": null,
      "title": null,
      "body": "Melhoria diária e paciência — nenhuma excelência é súbita.",
      "kind": "hipotese",
      "free_tags": [],
      "created_at": "2026-07-05T00:48:31.192006+00:00",
      "themes": [
        {
          "id": "0fa8086f-220f-4074-a418-110e623d8d85",
          "slug": "disciplina",
          "label": "Disciplina"
        },
        {
          "id": "2245f69c-e13f-45b5-848e-d79688d92909",
          "slug": "competencia",
          "label": "Competência"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "43936492-0133-4220-bff8-ecefbf3318d8",
      "book_id": "58f0ada6-ef80-4d2c-a68d-28c5d8467c78",
      "chapter_id": null,
      "title": null,
      "body": "O jogador dominado pelo medo força arremessos e perde a leitura do jogo — clareza vence ansiedade.",
      "kind": "hipotese",
      "free_tags": [],
      "created_at": "2026-07-05T00:48:31.192006+00:00",
      "themes": [
        {
          "id": "2a262e8b-ce32-4702-8252-89ecadd6d9ea",
          "slug": "razao",
          "label": "Razão"
        },
        {
          "id": "82d7190e-818e-427b-ad09-c22e996a3733",
          "slug": "medo",
          "label": "Medo"
        },
        {
          "id": "3ec9df17-f6ac-458b-813d-f1ffeb03be5e",
          "slug": "autocontrole",
          "label": "Autocontrole"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "cfabbc3d-2bbf-4f4c-8cb7-e9ab767792dd",
      "book_id": "58f0ada6-ef80-4d2c-a68d-28c5d8467c78",
      "chapter_id": null,
      "title": null,
      "body": "Jackson ensinava respiração e meditação antes de jogadas — observar os próprios pensamentos precede controlar a quadra.",
      "kind": "hipotese",
      "free_tags": [],
      "created_at": "2026-07-05T00:48:31.192006+00:00",
      "themes": [
        {
          "id": "0fa8086f-220f-4074-a418-110e623d8d85",
          "slug": "disciplina",
          "label": "Disciplina"
        },
        {
          "id": "3ec9df17-f6ac-458b-813d-f1ffeb03be5e",
          "slug": "autocontrole",
          "label": "Autocontrole"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "aab29c54-16b9-4c07-8edd-f2460bc308fe",
      "book_id": "58f0ada6-ef80-4d2c-a68d-28c5d8467c78",
      "chapter_id": null,
      "title": null,
      "body": "Jordan e Kobe só viraram campeões quando o ego passou a servir o grupo — o ego do craque é obstáculo, não ativo.",
      "kind": "hipotese",
      "free_tags": [],
      "created_at": "2026-07-05T00:48:31.192006+00:00",
      "themes": [
        {
          "id": "aedd75c6-593e-47fd-b31a-d9a8e4206af9",
          "slug": "identidade",
          "label": "Identidade"
        },
        {
          "id": "abfbc107-783c-472a-82e4-499aa36e9a18",
          "slug": "ego",
          "label": "Ego"
        },
        {
          "id": "71c544be-86cb-4b38-a754-0cae1abda757",
          "slug": "lideranca",
          "label": "Liderança"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "dddac9dd-4030-41cc-88c9-a66e95e69e49",
      "book_id": "58f0ada6-ef80-4d2c-a68d-28c5d8467c78",
      "chapter_id": null,
      "title": null,
      "body": "Repetir o básico milhares de vezes é o que cria liberdade dentro do jogo — a automação libera a criação.",
      "kind": "hipotese",
      "free_tags": [],
      "created_at": "2026-07-05T00:48:31.192006+00:00",
      "themes": [
        {
          "id": "0fa8086f-220f-4074-a418-110e623d8d85",
          "slug": "disciplina",
          "label": "Disciplina"
        },
        {
          "id": "2245f69c-e13f-45b5-848e-d79688d92909",
          "slug": "competencia",
          "label": "Competência"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "c89a36f0-fafa-496b-b569-463132763b43",
      "book_id": "58f0ada6-ef80-4d2c-a68d-28c5d8467c78",
      "chapter_id": null,
      "title": null,
      "body": "Jackson nunca gritava pra controlar — criava um ambiente onde o jogador queria entregar o melhor; a melhor liderança produz autonomia.",
      "kind": "hipotese",
      "free_tags": [],
      "created_at": "2026-07-05T00:48:31.192006+00:00",
      "themes": [
        {
          "id": "71c544be-86cb-4b38-a754-0cae1abda757",
          "slug": "lideranca",
          "label": "Liderança"
        },
        {
          "id": "3ec9df17-f6ac-458b-813d-f1ffeb03be5e",
          "slug": "autocontrole",
          "label": "Autocontrole"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "b741942d-c6a3-4c76-8031-887cbc819d5d",
      "book_id": "58f0ada6-ef80-4d2c-a68d-28c5d8467c78",
      "chapter_id": null,
      "title": null,
      "body": "Ler o jogo antes de decidir — a leitura precede a jogada, sempre.",
      "kind": "hipotese",
      "free_tags": [],
      "created_at": "2026-07-05T00:48:31.192006+00:00",
      "themes": [
        {
          "id": "2a262e8b-ce32-4702-8252-89ecadd6d9ea",
          "slug": "razao",
          "label": "Razão"
        },
        {
          "id": "2245f69c-e13f-45b5-848e-d79688d92909",
          "slug": "competencia",
          "label": "Competência"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "a3f79192-e3a7-40fe-b753-4e354c94bf34",
      "book_id": "58f0ada6-ef80-4d2c-a68d-28c5d8467c78",
      "chapter_id": null,
      "title": null,
      "body": "Campeonatos são consequência da cultura, não o alvo direto — construir a cultura produz a vitória.",
      "kind": "hipotese",
      "free_tags": [],
      "created_at": "2026-07-05T00:48:31.192006+00:00",
      "themes": [
        {
          "id": "71c544be-86cb-4b38-a754-0cae1abda757",
          "slug": "lideranca",
          "label": "Liderança"
        },
        {
          "id": "2245f69c-e13f-45b5-848e-d79688d92909",
          "slug": "competencia",
          "label": "Competência"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "bead244c-3cdb-4b50-b448-7a9c3a2dce79",
      "book_id": "58f0ada6-ef80-4d2c-a68d-28c5d8467c78",
      "chapter_id": null,
      "title": null,
      "body": "A emoção precisa existir, mas não dirigir a decisão — senti-la sem ser governado por ela.",
      "kind": "hipotese",
      "free_tags": [],
      "created_at": "2026-07-05T00:48:31.192006+00:00",
      "themes": [
        {
          "id": "2a262e8b-ce32-4702-8252-89ecadd6d9ea",
          "slug": "razao",
          "label": "Razão"
        },
        {
          "id": "3ec9df17-f6ac-458b-813d-f1ffeb03be5e",
          "slug": "autocontrole",
          "label": "Autocontrole"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "38465e03-9470-4b1a-8992-1f118ceb44bb",
      "book_id": "58f0ada6-ef80-4d2c-a68d-28c5d8467c78",
      "chapter_id": null,
      "title": null,
      "body": "A cultura do time nasce dos indivíduos — você muda o grupo mudando as pessoas.",
      "kind": "hipotese",
      "free_tags": [],
      "created_at": "2026-07-05T00:48:31.192006+00:00",
      "themes": [
        {
          "id": "aedd75c6-593e-47fd-b31a-d9a8e4206af9",
          "slug": "identidade",
          "label": "Identidade"
        },
        {
          "id": "71c544be-86cb-4b38-a754-0cae1abda757",
          "slug": "lideranca",
          "label": "Liderança"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "7bd45407-1d29-4872-9efb-59f0c07a16e3",
      "book_id": "58f0ada6-ef80-4d2c-a68d-28c5d8467c78",
      "chapter_id": null,
      "title": null,
      "body": "Jackson era calmo, nunca precisava provar autoridade — a confiança silenciosa dispensa demonstração.",
      "kind": "hipotese",
      "free_tags": [],
      "created_at": "2026-07-05T00:48:31.192006+00:00",
      "themes": [
        {
          "id": "71c544be-86cb-4b38-a754-0cae1abda757",
          "slug": "lideranca",
          "label": "Liderança"
        },
        {
          "id": "3ec9df17-f6ac-458b-813d-f1ffeb03be5e",
          "slug": "autocontrole",
          "label": "Autocontrole"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "66d62367-9442-48d6-8ec3-42ae2306035d",
      "book_id": "58f0ada6-ef80-4d2c-a68d-28c5d8467c78",
      "chapter_id": null,
      "title": null,
      "body": "Jogar por algo maior que si mesmo — o propósito coletivo dissolve o medo individual.",
      "kind": "hipotese",
      "free_tags": [],
      "created_at": "2026-07-05T00:48:31.192006+00:00",
      "themes": [
        {
          "id": "82d7190e-818e-427b-ad09-c22e996a3733",
          "slug": "medo",
          "label": "Medo"
        },
        {
          "id": "71c544be-86cb-4b38-a754-0cae1abda757",
          "slug": "lideranca",
          "label": "Liderança"
        },
        {
          "id": "7098acea-a6a9-4fba-951a-a861278a3ae2",
          "slug": "proposito",
          "label": "Propósito"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "4a62a324-97da-41c2-a621-4352f6ef4756",
      "book_id": "58f0ada6-ef80-4d2c-a68d-28c5d8467c78",
      "chapter_id": null,
      "title": null,
      "body": "Repetição e paciência — o campeonato é o topo de anos de base.",
      "kind": "hipotese",
      "free_tags": [],
      "created_at": "2026-07-05T00:48:31.192006+00:00",
      "themes": [
        {
          "id": "0fa8086f-220f-4074-a418-110e623d8d85",
          "slug": "disciplina",
          "label": "Disciplina"
        },
        {
          "id": "2245f69c-e13f-45b5-848e-d79688d92909",
          "slug": "competencia",
          "label": "Competência"
        }
      ]
